{"id":234197,"date":"2024-01-24T15:46:56","date_gmt":"2024-01-24T10:16:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=234197"},"modified":"2024-01-28T19:41:14","modified_gmt":"2024-01-28T14:11:14","slug":"narendra-bedi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/","title":{"rendered":"Narendra Bedi (Director) Wiki, Age, Death, Wife, Children, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-234254\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi.jpg\" alt=\"Narendra Bedi\" width=\"366\" height=\"458\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi.jpg 519w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 366px) 100vw, 366px\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<p>Narendra Bedi is an Indian filmmaker who predominantly worked in the Hindi film industry. Some of his popular films are Jawani Diwani (1972), Maha Chor (1976), and Adalat (1976).<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdfd1f3c82\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdfd1f3c82\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Wife_Children\" title=\"Wife &amp; Children\">Wife &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Film\" title=\"Film\">Film<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-bedi\/#Death\" title=\"Death\">Death<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Narendra Bedi was born in 1937 (<strong>age 45 years; at the time of death<\/strong>) in Bombay (now Mumbai), Maharashtra, British India. He completed a degree in Arts from the University of Mumbai, Maharashtra. Thereafter, he joined the film production team of G.P. Sippy who was a film director and producer in the Hindi film industry.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Narendra Bedi belongs to a Punjabi family.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Narendra Bedi&#8217;s father&#8217;s name is Rajinder Singh Bedi. He was an Indian writer and filmmaker. Narendra Bedi&#8217;s brother&#8217;s name is Rajkumar Bedi. He was a filmmaker in the Hindi film industry.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_211868\" style=\"width: 302px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajinder-Singh-Bedi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-211868\" class=\"wp-image-211868\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajinder-Singh-Bedi.jpg\" alt=\"Rajinder Singh Bedi\" width=\"292\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajinder-Singh-Bedi.jpg 586w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajinder-Singh-Bedi-220x300.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 292px) 100vw, 292px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-211868\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Narendra Bedi&#8217;s father Rajinder Singh Bedi<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife_Children\"><\/span><strong>Wife &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Narendra Bedi married Veena Devi. She was a costume designer and story writer by profession.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_234256\" style=\"width: 396px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-with-Veena-Devi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-234256\" class=\" wp-image-234256\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-with-Veena-Devi.jpg\" alt=\"Narendra Bedi with Veena Devi\" width=\"386\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-with-Veena-Devi.jpg 647w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-with-Veena-Devi-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Narendra-Bedi-with-Veena-Devi-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-234256\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Narendra Bedi with Veena Devi<\/p><\/div>\n<p>They have a daughter named <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ila-bedi-dutta\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ila Bedi Dutta<\/a> (eldest) and two sons <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/manek-bedi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manek Bedi<\/a> (elder) and <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rajat-bedi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rajat Bedi<\/a> (younger). Rajat Bedi and Manek Bedi are Indian actors and film producers in the Indian entertainment industry. Ila Bedi Dutta is a writer and film producer in the Hindi entertainment industry.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_211850\" style=\"width: 352px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajat-Bedi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-211850\" class=\"wp-image-211850\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajat-Bedi.jpg\" alt=\"Rajat Bedi\" width=\"342\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajat-Bedi.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Rajat-Bedi-288x300.jpg 288w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-211850\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rajat Bedi<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_211866\" style=\"width: 436px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Manek-Bedi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-211866\" class=\" wp-image-211866\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Manek-Bedi.jpg\" alt=\"Manek Bedi\" width=\"426\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Manek-Bedi.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Manek-Bedi-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Manek-Bedi-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-211866\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manek Bedi<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_211865\" style=\"width: 444px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Ila-Bedi-Dutta.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-211865\" class=\" wp-image-211865\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Ila-Bedi-Dutta.jpg\" alt=\"Ila Bedi Dutta\" width=\"434\" height=\"289\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Ila-Bedi-Dutta.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Ila-Bedi-Dutta-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Ila-Bedi-Dutta-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 434px) 100vw, 434px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-211865\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ila Bedi Dutta<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Film\"><\/span><strong>Film<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Narendra Bedi&#8217;s first film as a film director was the film Bandhan (1969). The film was produced by G.P. Sippy.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-poster-of-the-film-Bandhan.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-234273\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-poster-of-the-film-Bandhan.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-poster-of-the-film-Bandhan.jpg 495w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-poster-of-the-film-Bandhan-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Some of his other films were Jawani Diwani (1972), Khotey Sikkay (1974), Rafoo Chakkar -The Runaways (1975), Maha Chor (1976), and Akhri Sanghursh (1997).<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Death\"><\/span>Death<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Narendra Bedi died on 21 October 1982.<\/p>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Narendra Bedi is an Indian filmmaker who predominantly worked in the Hindi film industry. Some of his popular films are Jawani Diwani (1972), Maha Chor (1976), and Adalat (1976). Wiki\/Biography Narendra Bedi was born in 1937 (age 45 years; at the time of death) in Bombay (now Mumbai), Maharashtra, British India. He completed a degree in Arts from the University of Mumbai, Maharashtra. Thereafter, he joined the film production team of G.P. Sippy who was a film director and producer in the Hindi film industry. Family Narendra Bedi belongs to a Punjabi family. Parents &amp; Siblings Narendra Bedi&#8217;s father&#8217;s name <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":78,"featured_media":234254,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/234197"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/78"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=234197"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/234197\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":235107,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/234197\/revisions\/235107"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/234254"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=234197"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=234197"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=234197"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}